**In Laravel, the common convention is:**

Item	Convention	Example
Model	Singular	Event, Company, Saving, Credit
Controller	Singular + Controller	EventController, CompanyController, SavingController
Database Table	Plural	events, companies, savings, credits
Route Name	Usually plural	events.index, companies.store
View Folder	Usually plural	resources/views/events/


